long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Chrome extension to inspect and configure Mojito experiments. 
Mojito is a professional, open split testing stack for speed & security. This extension helps user to inspect and config experiments running on their sites.
See more details on https://mojito.mx/
